{
  "texts": [
    "These challenges can be addressed by building AI models that utilize digital medical records, which are abundantly available in our digitalized world.",
    "AI models can also easily collect data from medical journals and efficiently analyze electronic medical reports and clinical trial reports.",
    "This AI capability may be used to identify the best-suited individuals to be recruited for clinical trials.",
    "For example, AiCure is a mobile application that utilizes AI to monitor treatments in real time during clinical trials (Salcedo et al. 2021).",
    "Using digital biomarkers, this platform can monitor the engagement of patients and their response to the tested drug."
  ]
}